info.description:
pyLASlib
=============

**Development Status:** *Planning*

pyLASlib is a small Python package which provides reading, editing and writing LAS (Log ASCII Standart) 2.0 files.

pyLASlib is written according to LAS 2.0 specifications.

License
-------

pyLASlib is distributed under Apache License 2.0
